The paper is about improving the performance of image recognition through the design of deep networks. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions the ILSVRC 2012 benchmark, which is a popular benchmark in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
